        <mxCell id="qSaCKScujajxPJi203jA-1" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="Experiment 10: To design a Video Confrencing service(Zoom,Meet)" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="430" x="200" y="40" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="qSaCKScujajxPJi203jA-2" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="it is an online platform where multi users can connect with each other and share thheir audio and video" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="450" x="200" y="80" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="qSaCKScujajxPJi203jA-3" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="Functional requirements&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;li data-start=&quot;281&quot; data-end=&quot;353&quot;&gt;Users should be able to sign up, log in, and log out of the system.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li data-start=&quot;355&quot; data-end=&quot;455&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;Users should be able to create instant&amp;nbsp; with a unique meeting ID .&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li data-start=&quot;457&quot; data-end=&quot;565&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;Participants should be able to join meetings using a meeting link or meeting ID&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-start=&quot;567&quot; data-end=&quot;666&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;The system should allow real-time audio and video communication between multiple participants.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li data-start=&quot;668&quot; data-end=&quot;759&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;Users should be able to mute/unmute microphone and turn camera on/off during meetings.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-start=&quot;851&quot; data-end=&quot;936&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Users should be able to share their screen (full screen or specific window/tab).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li data-start=&quot;938&quot; data-end=&quot;1028&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;The system should provide an in-meeting chat feature for&amp;nbsp; and messaging.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="230" width="410" x="210" y="190" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="qSaCKScujajxPJi203jA-4" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="Non Functional requirements&lt;div&gt;&lt;li data-start=&quot;187&quot; data-end=&quot;290&quot;&gt;The system should support low latency (minimal delay) for real-time audio and video communication.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;li data-start=&quot;292&quot; data-end=&quot;365&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;The system should be highly available with uptime of at least 99.9%.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;li data-start=&quot;367&quot; data-end=&quot;460&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;The system should be scalable to handle a large number of concurrent users and meetings.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;li data-start=&quot;462&quot; data-end=&quot;556&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;The system should ensure secure communication using encryption (e.g., end-to-end or TLS).&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;li data-start=&quot;558&quot; data-end=&quot;650&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;The system should provide fast response time (e.g., meeting join within a few seconds).&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;li data-start=&quot;652&quot; data-end=&quot;750&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;The system should be reliable and maintain call stability even under poor network conditions.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;li data-start=&quot;752&quot; data-end=&quot;841&quot;&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="350" width="420" x="180" y="530" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="qSaCKScujajxPJi203jA-5" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="Core entities&lt;div&gt;&lt;li data-start=&quot;158&quot; data-end=&quot;292&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;161&quot; data-end=&quot;169&quot;&gt;User&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-start=&quot;294&quot; data-end=&quot;415&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;297&quot; data-end=&quot;308&quot;&gt;Meeting&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-start=&quot;417&quot; data-end=&quot;531&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;420&quot; data-end=&quot;435&quot;&gt;Participant&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-start=&quot;533&quot; data-end=&quot;634&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;536&quot; data-end=&quot;544&quot;&gt;Host&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-start=&quot;636&quot; data-end=&quot;728&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;639&quot; data-end=&quot;655&quot;&gt;Media Stream&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-start=&quot;730&quot; data-end=&quot;815&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;733&quot; data-end=&quot;749&quot;&gt;Chat Message&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="230" width="480" x="-30" y="870" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
