        <mxCell id="qSaCKScujajxPJi203jA-307" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="👉 Instead of everyone sending video to everyone (P2P),&lt;br data-start=&quot;269&quot; data-end=&quot;272&quot;&gt;&#xa;👉 Each user sends &lt;strong data-start=&quot;291&quot; data-end=&quot;316&quot;&gt;one stream to the SFU&lt;/strong&gt;,&lt;br data-start=&quot;317&quot; data-end=&quot;320&quot;&gt;&#xa;👉 SFU &lt;strong data-start=&quot;327&quot; data-end=&quot;361&quot;&gt;forwards that stream to others&lt;/strong&gt;." vertex="1">
