        <mxCell id="qSaCKScujajxPJi203jA-322" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;li data-start=&quot;342&quot; data-end=&quot;405&quot;&gt;Every user sends their &lt;strong data-start=&quot;368&quot; data-end=&quot;385&quot;&gt;audio + video&lt;/strong&gt; to the MCU server&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-start=&quot;406&quot; data-end=&quot;438&quot;&gt;&#xa;MCU &lt;strong data-start=&quot;413&quot; data-end=&quot;436&quot;&gt;decodes all streams&lt;/strong&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-start=&quot;439&quot; data-end=&quot;499&quot;&gt;&#xa;It &lt;strong data-start=&quot;445&quot; data-end=&quot;463&quot;&gt;mixes/combines&lt;/strong&gt; them into one (like a grid video)&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-start=&quot;500&quot; data-end=&quot;575&quot;&gt;&#xa;Then &lt;strong data-start=&quot;508&quot; data-end=&quot;525&quot;&gt;encodes again&lt;/strong&gt; and sends a &lt;strong data-start=&quot;538&quot; data-end=&quot;560&quot;&gt;single stream back&lt;/strong&gt; to each user&lt;/li&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="170" width="400" x="485" y="7050" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
